CONTRIBUTOR CREDITS
===================

This project was built with the assistance of Claude AI (Haiku 4.5), an advanced
coding assistant developed by Anthropic. Claude's capabilities in architecture
design, full-stack development, security analysis, and vendor-neutral platform
design were instrumental in building this comprehensive enterprise platform.

Original Concept & Direction: Fractional PM
Development & Architecture: Claude AI (Coding Agent)
Testing & Deployment: Community Contributors

